column4: Intel lifts forecasts as driverless tech  AI add to PC gains
column5: Chipmaker Intel Corp raised its full-year revenue and profit forecasts on higher expectations for its mainstay personal computer business and growth in newer areas such as artificial intelligence and autonomous driving.
